emuInput.TitMainTitle: Eight Alpha Kappa Alpha debutantes, from left: Connie L. Young, Janyce Murray, Helen Adair, Sylvia Wofford, Jacqueline "Jackie" Lewis [Jacqui Thompson], Yvonne Holt, Carolyn Ann Key, and Patty Lou Redwood, standing behind table with light colored lace tablecloth and teacups for social tea, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 5, 1955, pg. 11, reads: "AKA Debutantes - At the initial get-together of the 1955 debs, tea was served by Jacqueline Lewis, last year's debutante queen. Left to right: Connie L. Young, Janyce Murray, Helen Adair, Sylvia Wofford, Miss Lewis, Yvonne Holt, Carolyn Ann Key and Patty Lou Redwood.  Not pictured are Barbara Mason, Beverly Loftin, Alfreda Turner and Barbara Smith. - Harris Photo."
